PREREQUISITES

In order to run log4j-converter you need

- Java version 1.5 or better

- Java must be on the path, or JAVA_HOME environment variable must be set

DOWNLOAD

The latest binaries and sources of this application should always be
available at the following web site:

http://code.google.com/p/log4j-properties-converter/


REPORTING BUGS AND PROBLEMS

